Academic Programs
Comprehensive Offerings:
The University of Novi Sad Serbia  offers a wide array of undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral programs across various fields, including but not limited to:
Natural Sciences
Engineering
Social Sciences
Humanities
Medicine
